fields.name: Calathea Orbifolia
fields.description: A South American prayer plant kept for its clean, designer-quality foliage, Orbifolia is one of the largest Calatheas. Its bold oval leaves can grow over a foot across – it makes a classic statement plant.

fields.name: Mid Century Walnut Sideboard
fields.description: Rosewood credenza with dovetail construction & round tapered legs. Eight outer drawers with rounded handles. Center door opens to reveal five additional drawers inside. Dimensions: 75.5"L | 19"D | 32"H

fields.name: Fiddle Leaf Fig
fields.description: Fiddle Leaf Figs, 'Ficus Lyrata', are gorgeous plants known for their large leaves and vibrant green colors.   With their big broad leaves, the fiddle leaf fig is definitely one of the most iconic house plants out there.

fields.name: Burgundy Rubber Plant
fields.description: The Burgundy Rubber Tree is easy for beginners and a great starter plant! They can quickly grow up to 8' inside and do best in bright to moderate indirect light.

fields.name: Concrete Planter Gray
fields.description: This round planter is made from concrete material in a neutral gray tone, a great addition to your indoor or outdoor plant display.

fields.name: Smart Growbar
fields.description: Our Growbar is the vital solution for creating a lush plantscape in sun-deprived spaces. Its full spectrum LED grow light nourishes low-to-bright light loving plants.

fields.name: Instant Plant Food Indoor & Houseplant Fertilizer
fields.description: Specially crafted for all types of houseplants including indoor plants, tropicals, orchids, air plants, desert plants, potted plants, balcony or windowsill planters and self-watering containers. Use it on a new plant or to revitalize old ones.

fields.name: Durham Plant Stand - Set of 2
fields.description: Take your favorite plants out from the wild and into your living room with this 2-piece set of plant stands. Inspired by mid-century modern details, each stand sits on an x-frame base with four mango wood feet.

fields.name: 4-Pack Macrame Plant Hanger
fields.description: Fit Various Pot Sizes - Our 4-Pack Macramé Plant Hangers can fit small and large pots of up to 10 inches

fields.name: Majestic Palm
fields.description: Majestic Palm (Ravenea rivularis) has upward-arching narrow, pinnately compound leaves arranged up the stem. As the breeze blows through their leaves, they have a waving, graceful look that catches the eye.
